10 (i) Sooner than 9 months following the later of:
11 1. The date that the individual first obtains the learner’s
12 instructional permit; or
13 2. The most recent date the individual was convicted of, or
14 granted probation before judgment under § 6–220 of the Criminal Procedure Article for, a
